To run tests:
	Set up testing by running 'cmake ..' in /build.
	Run tests with 'reset && make -j2 && mv build/test/unit/unit . && gdb --args ./unit'

compiler flags to try for optimization:
-ffinite-math-only -fno-signed-zeros -ffast-math
-Ofast
-fno-exceptions -fno-rtti -flto(or unity build)
-fimplicit-constexpr

profile guided optimization (build technique)
LLVM bolt

to check for branch mispredictions with profiler
perf stat exe

libc++ debug mode
GLIBCXX_DEBUG (macro)

optimizations to try : Boost::graph

PerAreaPerFactionData is created on demand and never destroyed.
